ITALIAN WINES

Many wine drinkers are now turning to Italy to provide good wine at modest cost. We have taken the challenge seriously, and have searched out the best that Italy has to offer. We particularly commend the litres and double-litres as among the best values in good red and white wine for the money—the Ghemme, for a glorious, big red—and the Soave, for your daily warm weather wine.
